videos.headline: Taylor pounds through the line for Badgers TD
videos.description: Wisconsin RB Jonathan Taylor finds the perfect hole and goes through for a 4-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor pounds through the line for Badgers TD) 2019/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Badgers block punt, come out with safety
videos.description: After Central Michigan's punter fumbles the ball, a Wisconsin defender touches the ball as it goes out of bounds, resulting in a safety.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Badgers block punt, come out with safety) 2019/09/07

videos.headline: Taylor walks in for 2nd touchdown in 1st quarter
videos.description: Wisconsin RB Jonathan Taylor gets in unblocked for his second TD in the first quarter to put the Badgers ahead 16-0.

videos.headline: Wisconsin gets INT, scores on tip-toe pass
videos.description: Badgers big man Jack Sanborn reads Central Michigan QB Quinten Dormandy perfectly for the pick, then RB Jonathan Taylor shows off his balance and speed with a 17-yard TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin gets INT, scores on tip-toe pass) 2019/09/07
